    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790560/extras/0b76d7f3f8dfc224aa4e93bc9fc46148.avif?t=1639470580\" width=600 height=225 /></span><br>在2070年，神秘物体袭击了南极洲，融化了无边的冰川，淹没了整个世界，破坏了大气层。这导致人类分裂成许多部族，学会了如何在水下生存。其中一些人类发展、提高了能量并开始控制大部分资源。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790560/extras/3cfaf0f541802d4a8bd9b84452efac44.webp?t=1639470580\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790560/extras/80f60132251760106340f2aec46afa7e.poster.avif?t=1639470580\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790560/extras/80f60132251760106340f2aec46afa7e.webm?t=1639470580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790560/extras/80f60132251760106340f2aec46afa7e.mp4?t=1639470580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你必须从不同分数的几个角色的面孔上找出2112年勇士族和海盗族发生严重冲突的事件。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790560/extras/3cfaf0f541802d4a8bd9b84452efac44.webp?t=1639470580\" width=600 height=10 /></span><br><br>在游戏中呈现了许多未来的技术，通过使用这些技术，你将能够应对敌人和完成任务。此外，有有趣的故事情节转折和罕见的水下世界的全貌。故事由5个章节组成，你将能够操作不同的潜艇设备。",
